Core Capabilities
- Supports 4K video editing with real-time playback and rendering.
- Offers over 300 visual effects and filters for enhanced creativity.
- Includes advanced audio editing tools with noise removal and equalizer features.
- Features motion tracking for precise subject following in videos.
- Provides multi-track timeline for seamless organization of video and audio layers.

